text: Vlad Andrei Danale (born 28 January 1998) is a Romanian professional footballer who plays as a forward for Aerostar Bacău, on loan from Politehnica Iași. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Iași Category:Romanian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Liga I players Category:FC Politehnica Iași (2010) players Category:Liga II players Category:CS Aerostar Bacău players
